      "score": 6,
      "comments": 0,
      "author": "diktomat",
      "published": "2026-05-23T15:11:47Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Use ephemeral GitHub Actions runners (`--ephemeral`) to ensure clean build environments and prevent persistent state security exploits between jobs.",
        "Deploy Actions Runner Controller (ARC) on Kubernetes to auto-scale runner pods dynamically based on webhook events and workflow demands.",
        "Leverage Docker-in-Docker (DinD) or rootless container engines safely within runner environments to support containerized workflow steps efficiently."
      ]
    },
